item.title: Edgware Martial Arts Academy
item.description:
Edgware Martial Arts Academy

Q: What style of martial art will I learn? A: You will learn Choi Kwang-Do (CKD), a revolutionary martial art and exercise programme developed by Grandmaster Kwang Jo Choi. The martial art is founded on the principle that self defence techniques should generate maximum force, be practical and easy to learn, enhance your health as you practice, as well as develop physical and mental conditioning.
